1 general appearance, 2 hind wing, 3 maxillae and labium, 4 mandible, 5 labrum, 6 antenna, 7 abdomen, 8 hind leg. Scales 1 mm (Figs 1, 7), 0.5 mm (Figs 6, 8), 0.25 mm (Figs 2–5).
